sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as OGXServerValidator<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Reconciler as OGXServerReconciler
    participant Config as ogx-operator-config<br/>ConfigMap
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Pipeline
    participant OGXServer as OGX Server Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,OGXServer: Flow 1: OGXServer Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply OGXServer CR
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-ogx-io-v1beta1-ogxserver<br/>TLS, K8s API Auth
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admit / Reject
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR created/rejected

    K8sAPI->>Reconciler: Watch event (OGXServer changed)<br/>TLS 1.2+, ServiceAccount token
    Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Read OGXServer spec<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    Reconciler->>Config: Read image overrides<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    Reconciler->>Kustomize: Render manifests
    Kustomize-->>Reconciler: Deployment, Service, SA,<br/>PVC, NP, HPA, PDB, RB
    Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Create/Update managed resources<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token

    loop Health Check Polling
        Reconciler->>OGXServer: GET /v1/health<br/>HTTP/8321, No Auth
        OGXServer-->>Reconciler: Health status
        Reconciler->>OGXServer: GET /v1/providers<br/>HTTP/8321, No Auth
        OGXServer-->>Reconciler: Provider info
        Reconciler->>OGXServer: GET /v1/version<br/>HTTP/8321, No Auth
        OGXServer-->>Reconciler: Version info
    end

    Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Update OGXServer status<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token

    Note over Reconciler,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Legacy Resource Adoption

    Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Find legacy LlamaStackDistribution<br/>HTTPS/443
    K8sAPI-->>Reconciler: Legacy Deployment found
    Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Scale down legacy Deployment (replicas=0)<br/>HTTPS/443
    Note over Reconciler: Wait for pods to terminate<br/>(release RWO PVC locks)
    Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Strip old ownerRef from PVC<br/>HTTPS/443
    Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Label PVC for new controller<br/>HTTPS/443
    Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Transfer Service/Ingress ownerRefs<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Reconciler,K8sAPI: Flow 3: CA Bundle Assembly

    Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Read user CA ConfigMaps<br/>(spec.tls.trust.caCertificates)
    K8sAPI-->>Reconciler: PEM certificates
    Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Read odh-trusted-ca-bundle ConfigMap
    K8sAPI-->>Reconciler: Platform CA certs
    Note over Reconciler: Validate X.509 certs<br/>Strip non-cert blocks<br/>Enforce 10MB / 1000 cert limits
    Reconciler->>K8sAPI: Create/Update {instance}-ca-bundle ConfigMap
